nodes.text: Star Wars: Dark Times—Out of the Wilderness

Star Wars: Dark Times—Out of the Wilderness is the fifth arc in the Star Wars: Dark Times series of comics. It consists of five regular comic issues published as a miniseries with its own numbering, with the first released in August of 2011.

Dass Jennir, one of the few Jedi survivors of Order 66, is on the run from the Empire, and his chief pursuer is none other than Darth Vader! To make matters worse, a mysterious bounty hunter and his killer droid are also hunting Jennir, while Jennir's former comrades from the smuggling ship Uhumele are hoping for a reunion. The paths of all parties are fated to cross, and when they do, prepare for a collision!
